acceptance_criteria: "A focused public document dated 2026-07-11 cites current official OpenAI plugin, Apps SDK, security, testing, deployment, and submission sources; distinguishes a plugin from an app and local Codex from ChatGPT web/public distribution; records live repository and isolated cache-install findings; identifies verified gaps and non-gaps; provides target layouts, file-by-file phases, security and tool-contract requirements, test matrices, rollout gates, and proposed pm decomposition; docs index and Codex router link it; no plugin implementation artifact changes."
value: "Future implementation can proceed from verified product terminology, current official sources, exact repository evidence, and testable acceptance gates instead of assumptions."
