comments[5]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-11T11:10:58.363Z",codex-native-plugin-research,"Duplicate-check evidence: all-status searches performed for the exact July 2026 pm-codex, Apps SDK, ChatGPT plugin, official docs, and cache fallback concepts returned no existing research/documentation task. Closed pm-0c9q and pm-d97r remain prior shipped lineage; this docs-only task is the scoped first child of pm-95d7."
  "2026-07-11T11:11:10.197Z",codex-native-plugin-research,"Scope checkpoint: Current Codex CLI 0.144.1 proof shows the repo marketplace installs pm-codex 2026.7.11 and registers pm-mcp. Research has also proven the installed cache lacks dist/dependencies and its launcher falls back to npx @unbrained/pm-cli@latest; the bundle has no app wiring or hosted HTTP MCP path; commands/ is not a documented Codex plugin component; current MCP tools lack Apps SDK output schemas and safety annotations. Documentation only in this task."
  "2026-07-11T11:13:00.448Z",codex-native-plugin-research,"Validator evidence: uv run --with pyyaml python /home/steve/.codex/skills/.system/plugin-creator/scripts/validate_plugin.py plugins/pm-codex fails six checks. Each of pm-auditor, pm-native, and pm-release declares icon_small and icon_large as ./assets/pm-cli-small.svg relative to the skill root, but only plugins/pm-codex/assets/pm-cli-small.svg exists. Current Codex installation tolerance does not replace validator compliance."
  "2026-07-11T11:21:55.914Z",codex-native-plugin-research,"Official-source evidence (opened live 2026-07-11): OpenAI Codex Plugins and Build Plugins; ChatGPT Build an app and Submit plugins; Apps SDK overview, tool planning, MCP server, authentication, deployment, ChatGPT connection, testing, MCP Apps compatibility, security/privacy, reference, and changelog; Secure MCP Tunnel; and Codex changelog. The report links each canonical official URL and records the observed developers.openai.com to learn.chatgpt.com redirects."
  "2026-07-11T11:21:56.563Z",codex-native-plugin-research,"Verification evidence: pm-linked pnpm build passed; pm-linked pnpm quality:docs-skills passed; pnpm quality:static passed, including static quality and the 14-surface token-budget gate; git diff --check passed; pm health --check-only --summary passed with zero warnings; pm validate history_drift passed with zero drift. Its only warning is pre-existing repository debt: 278 legacy closed items missing resolution metadata. Changed product files are documentation only: docs/CHATGPT_CODEX_PLUGIN_IMPLEMENTATION.md, docs/CODEX_PLUGIN.md, and docs/README.md; plugin runtime, manifest, assets, and tests remain untouched."
